snippet.title: Star Wars: Jedi Knight - Dark Forces II (1997) - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The cinematic trailer to the seminal first/third person shooter by Lucasarts, with the man who REALLY stole the Death Star plans ;)

For more information, visit:
http://www.mobygames.com/game/windows/star-wars-jedi-knight-dark-forces-ii
